00338 void MapFrame::mouseMoveEvent( QMouseEvent* e)
00339 {
00340 
00341         int x=e->x();
00342         int y=e->y();
00343         
00344 
00345         // latitude and longitude
00346         int height=frameRect().height();
00347         double dLatitude = int( 10 * ( ( -180.0/(height -1) ) * y + 90.0 ) )/10.0;
00348 
00349         int width=frameRect().width();
00350         double dLongitude = int( 10 * ( ( 360.0/(width -1) ) * x - 180.0 ) )/10.0;
00351 
00352 
00353         //Change tool tip       
00354         QString country= Country(x,y);
00355         
00356         if (!(country=="EMPTY"))
00357                 QToolTip::showText(e->globalPos(),country);
00358         else
00359                 QToolTip::showText(e->globalPos(),"");
00360 
00361         emit positionChanged(dLongitude,dLatitude);
00362 }
